From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Plecra <marli@frost.red>
Date: Sun, 19 Jul 2026 20:06:33 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] Implement type variables with a new Universe judgement.

We also extend the construction of the context index of the derivation check to ensure it doesnt introduce any type variables implicitly.
---
